### Step 5: Add constrained tool replacement

Replace a generic `fetch_url` (accepts any URL) with a constrained `load_document` (validates against an approved domain list). The generic version accepts `evil-site.com/malware.exe` without complaint. The constrained version rejects it before fetching.

```python
