B) The new developer needs to copy the senior developer's CLAUDE.md to their own home directory.
C) User-level CLAUDE.md (~/.claude/CLAUDE.md) applies only to that user — it is not shared with teammates via version control. Move the coding standards to the project-level .claude/CLAUDE.md or root CLAUDE.md so they are checked into the repository.
