</details>

**Q57 (Task 5.5).** Your extraction system achieves 96% overall accuracy on your test set. Management wants to fully automate all extractions without human review. Before agreeing, what validation should you perform?

A) Run the system on a larger test set to confirm the 96% holds.
B) Compare accuracy against a competitor's system to validate the benchmark.
C) Analyze accuracy by document type and field to verify consistent performance across all segments — aggregate accuracy may mask poor performance on specific document types or fields that could cause systematic downstream errors.
